## ğŸ¤” Why FindaLedge?

- Vector search (semantic) and keyword search (BM25) each have strengths and weaknesses.
- **FindaLedge** combines both (ensemble search) for best accuracy, with zero setup hassle.
- Handles all the plumbing: document loading, chunking, embedding, index sync, result fusion (RRF), and more!

## âœ¨ Features

| Feature | Description |
|---|---|
| ğŸ¯ Hybrid Search | Combines vector & keyword search (BM25) with RRF fusion |
| ğŸ”Œ Flexible | Supports Chroma, FAISS, BM25s, OpenAI, Ollama, HuggingFace, etc. |
| ğŸ“š Easy Ingestion | Add files, directories, or LangChain Documents instantly |
| ğŸ”„ Auto Indexing | Indices are auto-created, updated, and persisted |
| ğŸ§¹ Simple API | Add, search, remove documents with one-liners |
| ğŸ§© LangChain Ready | Use as a Retriever in LangChain chains |
| ğŸ§ª Full Test Suite | 100+ tests, pytest/uv compatible |

## âš™ï¸ Supported Environment

| Item | Supported |
|---|---|
| Python | 3.11+ (Windows/Powershellæ¨å¥¨) |
